name: Uni-iq
biography: Uni-iq is a woman from Oulu, Finland, but her native language is English. He has always been in music class at school, where he has been a singer. He has also sung in front of large audiences. He enjoys dancing in clubs. On the other hand, rap music is close to his heart.
vibe_of_voice: The raspy sound of a smoker
vocalist_visual: A beautiful slender woman, but slightly shorter than average. Likes make-up, piercings and tattoos. When she was younger, she used to have long blonde hair, but nowadays she has a pink mohawk.
